OL,5,G0330 Bread
OL,6,     FCarla Lane of the 'Liver Birds'
OL,7,     Fturned her attention back to
OL,8,     FLiverpool in the 1980s sitcom.
OL,9,     FBilly soon learns that opals are
OL,10,     Fbad luck when he buys a ring for
OL,11,     Fgirlfriend Julie.
OL,12,G0405 Bread
OL,13,     FLaughs and some outrageous 80s
OL,14,     Ffashions with the close-knit
OL,15,     FLiverpudlian family. Freddie's
OL,16,     Fmistress leaves him, but he
OL,17,     Fdecides to pay her a visit anyway.
